### Hadith 2:771

*Narrated Zaid bin Jubair:*

I saw Ibn 'Umar passing by a man who had made his Badana sit to
slaughter it. Ibn 'Umar said, "Slaughter it while it is standing with
one leg tied up as is the tradition of Muhammad."

